Uses of Package
gui.components.icon

  • Packages that use gui.components.icon 
    Package Description
    backend
    Contains the behind the scenes classes utilized by PEMS.
    backend.storage
    Set of classes used to represent the structure of the /cases/ directory managed by PEMS.
    backend.storage.file.img
    Consists of only one eponymous class: Img.
    gui.components
    Comprehensive package encompassing all graphics components designed specifically for use within the PEMS GUI.
    gui.components.icon
    Package containing the class for the ImgIcon component, as well as its subclasses.
    gui.display.dialogues
    Package containing classes for the various custom GUI dialogues displayed by PEMS.
    gui.display.editimg
    Contains classes for the image editing user interface.
    gui.display.finish
    Contains FinishPanel, the screen displayed when the user finishes editing a given case.
    gui.display.select
    Contains SelectPanel, the primary user interface for evidence file importation.
    gui.display.start
    Contains StartPanel, the initial screen displayed upon running PEMS.
